title: HMS LINCS Center Seeding Density Project
description: The density- and context-dependent sensitivities of 6 breast cancer cell lines plated at 6 different cell densities were assayed by the HMS LINCS Center by measuring cell counts using imaging 72 hours after treatment with each of 12 small molecule inhibitors across a 9-point dose range. For further information about the assay and reagents and to download the this dataset \(HMS LINCS Dataset [#20258](http://lincs.hms.harvard.edu/db/datasets/20258/)) or the cell count datasets from which the reported dose-response metrics were calculated \(HMS LINCS Datasets [#20256](http://lincs.hms.harvard.edu/db/datasets/20256/) and [#20257](http://lincs.hms.harvard.edu/db/datasets/20257/)), please visit the HMS LINCS Database.
